An ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the ","type":"text"},{"code":"isError","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" flag is risen.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Accessibility considerations","type":"heading","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for checkbox.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Cases forbidden by design","type":"heading","anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design"},{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error or a read only situation and a disabled component.","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Code samples","type":"heading","anchor":"Code-samples"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have a selected checkbox","    @Published var isOn: Bool = true","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, no error, not in read only mode","    OUDSCheckbox(isOn: $isOn, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\")","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, but is an error context","    OUDSCheckbox(isOn: $isOn, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable an error-related checkbox as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSCheckbox(isOn: $isOn, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"]},{"level":2,"text":"Suggestions","type":"heading","anchor":"Suggestions"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"According to the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-checkbox","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", the checkbox by default must be used in unselected state."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Design documentation","type":"heading","anchor":"Design-documentation"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-checkbox","type":"reference","isActive":true,"overridingTitle":"unified-design-system.orange.com","overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unified-design-system.orange.com"}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Themes rendering","anchor":"Themes-rendering"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Orange","anchor":"Orange"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkbox_Orange"}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Orange Compact","anchor":"Orange-Compact"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkbox_OrangeCompact"}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Sosh","anchor":"Sosh"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkbox_Sosh"}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Wireframe","anchor":"Wireframe"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkbox_Wireframe"}]},{"name":"Version","type":"aside","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"2.4.0 (Figma component design version)"}],"type":"paragr